caption: I wish he didn't know so many girls, so then maybe I would actually stand a chance. I don't have a good body or a flawless face like them, but I can give you so much more than they can, and it upsets me so much that you'll never understand that. But I'm not allowed to like you, because you're my best friend, and you're about to get involved with someone else. I just wish I could be more confident. #help #whatdoido
